{"tid":1398350,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［油尖旺街坊意見］奧海城其實唔差 開波/走佬都係","createTime":"2019-08-02T18:35:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T03:01:12.000Z","uid":197691,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a8d64bcdbb402e12d4fa8c0dbe002b44a09c4cd7","tid":1398350,"uid":197691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T18:35:24.000Z","msg":"大家可以睇睇奧海城嘅位置先<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uE0jBNW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuE0jBNW.png&h=93e34e39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1:走佬無限可能</span></strong><br />\n入到商場 你可以唔洗落地<br />\n就由<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大角咀行到旺角</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">仲要周圍都有大量出口<br />\n你係富榮花園落扮街坊又得<br />\n行去HSBC扮放工都得<br />\n再唔係入返櫻桃街公園不反對通知書位置亦得</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">而且奧運站係奧海城中間<br />\n你上到車轉紅色線又得<br />\n過海返香港站都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2:重現新城市之戰？</span></strong><br />\n奧海城同奧運站嘅連接中間<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">有個好撚大嘅中庭<br />\n三樓都可以唔小心放野落地下</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v9vGQcA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv9vGQcA.jpg&h=25f411f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個係奧運站入口前面<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WO7eqLW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWO7eqLW.jpg&h=b2799080&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想知再講"},{"pid":"fe840e49461b2bca629a0b9602d3f85350bb91d5","tid":1398350,"uid":197691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T18:39:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3f7a594aeb2668ff85e2158c22f07c71aa1ad827","tid":1398350,"uid":197691,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T18:39:59.000Z","msg":"住左10幾年<br />\n真心覺得奧海城玩得過"},{"pid":"30435feac4fbf35182376e852b4160c91d9b2a2e","tid":1398350,"uid":197691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T18:40:54.000Z","msg":"試下十年"},{"pid":"1c4da917e6ec0483f6cbae849feafb46f34328a3","tid":1398350,"uid":28831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T18:42:17.000Z","msg":"但比狗封曬出口就困嚴鬥<br />\n入面要人多先得"},{"pid":"f5a78e240c7b31c00d04481b8d5ebd825b8d321d","tid":1398350,"uid":180317,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T18:42:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd88b65c237ab18e8180c85b03635c29512c24d4","tid":1398350,"uid":197691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30435feac4fbf35182376e852b4160c91d9b2a2e","tid":1398350,"uid":197691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T18:40:54.000Z","msg":"試下十年"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T18:42:41.000Z","msg":"連<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3605f0e60b3b4891f364f620c4074fadf8b1e29c","tid":1398350,"uid":197691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c4da917e6ec0483f6cbae849feafb46f34328a3","tid":1398350,"uid":28831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T18:42:17.000Z","msg":"但比狗封曬出口就困嚴鬥<br />\n入面要人多先得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T18:43:58.000Z","msg":"2期有十幾個出口<br />\n仲可以行奧運站入一期<br />\n你死都唔入去嘅話就真係走唔到啦"},{"pid":"ea1768f0c3e21aaaf43caa75bd792cb314e1112c","tid":1398350,"uid":96,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T18:44:16.000Z","msg":"再唔係入返櫻桃街公園不反對通知書位置亦得<br />\n<br />\n不反對通知書等於廢左架啦<br />\n上